{"id":25783,"date":"2024-02-01T21:09:51","date_gmt":"2021-10-01T15:39:51","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=25783"},"modified":"2024-02-09T09:57:58","modified_gmt":"2024-02-09T04:27:58","slug":"luxury-bedroom-furniture-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/luxury-bedroom-furniture-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Luxury Bedroom Furniture Ideas That Will Catch Your Eye"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Modern luxury bedroom furniture can provide you with an equal dose of aesthetic appeal and serenity even without overspending. Want to know how? Keep reading<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Since your bedroom is a place of relaxation and rejuvenation after a long day\u2019s work, you must make it look refreshing and peaceful. Luxury doesn\u2019t always mean using high-end materials or finishes; it can also be equated to a \u2018feeling\u2019. Hence, transforming a drab bedroom into a luxurious space shouldn\u2019t be considered a mammoth task at all.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some of the benefits of using royal luxury bedroom furniture:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>It is structured and built keeping human ergonomics and comfort in mind (~health benefits).<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>It lends a timeless look to the bedroom (quality outlives trends).<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>It is multipurpose as it makes use of smart storage solutions.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>It increases the resale value of your home\/apartment, so consider it as an investment.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>It is affordable as it has a competitive price (~many luxury furniture brands currently).&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>It helps you express your individuality and personal style while remaining functional and practical.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>It is made of high-quality materials and is available in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/space-saving-bedroom-furniture\/\">space-saving designs<\/a>, so it is long-lasting and durable.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>It is now time to look at the latest luxury <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/latest-bedroom-furniture-design\/\">bedroom furniture designs<\/a> that are doing the rounds among prospective homeowners.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Luxury Bedroom Furniture Idea #1<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Swap your current <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/bedside-table-designs\/\">bedside tables<\/a> with luxury-finish side cabinets with drawers. They lend a glossy and royal vibe to the space when it is hit by the natural sunlight or ambient lighting on the inside. The statement art pieces hanging against the green accent wall also create an interesting focal point in the bedroom. Create a window seat area to read your book or have some hot coffee if you have extra space on the sides of your bed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210721\/modern-luxury-bedroom-furniture.jpg\" alt=\"Modern luxury bedroom furniture drawer and side cabinets in glossy finish lend a royal vibe\" class=\"wp-image-25789\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210721\/modern-luxury-bedroom-furniture.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210721\/modern-luxury-bedroom-furniture-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210721\/modern-luxury-bedroom-furniture-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210721\/modern-luxury-bedroom-furniture-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Place your vanity in line with your wardrobe and give it the same finish so that they look like one unit<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Luxury Bedroom Furniture Idea #2<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Different kinds of accessories can add a different type of personality and charm to the bedroom. This ergonomic bed with a dark wood bed frame\/headboard and chair for the study table can serve as luxury <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/kids-bedroom-interiors\/kids-bedroom-furniture-ideas\/\">childrens\u2019 bedroom furniture<\/a>.&nbsp; The area rug, furniture pieces and art wall have matching colour schemes, which give the children\u2019s bedroom a more cohesive and unified look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210704\/luxury-childrens-bedroom-furniture.jpg\" alt=\"Luxury children's bedroom study furniture in wood and blue laminate finish gives a unified look\" class=\"wp-image-25786\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210704\/luxury-childrens-bedroom-furniture.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210704\/luxury-childrens-bedroom-furniture-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210704\/luxury-childrens-bedroom-furniture-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210704\/luxury-childrens-bedroom-furniture-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The white and blue design theme of the bedroom gives it an airy and breezy vibe<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Customise your bed and enjoy up to 25 year warranty\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/08210059\/customise-your-bed-enjoy-up-to-25-year-warranty.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Luxury Bedroom Furniture Idea #3<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The luxury furniture pieces in this bedroom, that is, the purple faux-leather armchair and seating area near the window, the wooden bed with a high cushioned headboard and a bench in front, provide you with ultimate comfort and warmth. The entire setup of this luxury bedroom brings in the countryside vibe.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210715\/luxury-master-bedroom-furniture.jpg\" alt=\"Luxury master bedroom furniture, bed with a high cushioned headboard and purple faux-leather armchair\" class=\"wp-image-25788\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210715\/luxury-master-bedroom-furniture.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210715\/luxury-master-bedroom-furniture-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210715\/luxury-master-bedroom-furniture-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210715\/luxury-master-bedroom-furniture-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Appropriate pendant lighting fixtures can also add more sophistication to the luxury bedroom interiors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Luxury Bedroom Furniture Idea #4<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This master bedroom features luxury contemporary bedroom furniture pieces which make a bold and beautiful statement. This stylish headboard made up of elegant fabric instantly increases the glam factor of the bedroom. The built-in wardrobe with translucent sliding doors provides easy access to your clothes, shoes and other accessories. The well-cushioned bed and armchair by the window bring an air of relaxation into the room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210709\/luxury-contemporary-bedroom-furniture.jpg\" alt=\"Luxury contemporary bedroom furniture, the bedroom has a built-in wardrobe with translucent sliding doors\" class=\"wp-image-25787\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210709\/luxury-contemporary-bedroom-furniture.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210709\/luxury-contemporary-bedroom-furniture-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210709\/luxury-contemporary-bedroom-furniture-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210709\/luxury-contemporary-bedroom-furniture-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Adding greenery to the bedroom in the form of small potted plants quickly upgrades your room with a more expensive look without much effort, money and time<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Luxury Bedroom Furniture Idea #5<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you have too many clothes and shoes to wear but are running out of space? Don\u2019t worry! This high-rise bed with smart storage compartments and drawers underneath is the perfect solution for you.&nbsp; It increases the functionality of the bedroom and visually declutters it too. The bedside tables look sleek and fabulous against the yellow-painted walls. The abstract wall art blends in well with the interiors of the bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210658\/luxury-bedroom-furniture-india.jpg\" alt=\"Luxury bedroom furniture in India has smart storage compartments and drawers underneath the bed\" class=\"wp-image-25785\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/01210658\/luxury-bedroom-furniture-india.